      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "The gitian binaries are currently compiled with gcc-8, however the guix ones with gcc-9, which has the memcmp bug (#20005)? Given that gcc-11 has been released (presumably with a fix for that), would it make sense to use gcc-11 over gcc-9 for guix?\r\n\r\nFor reference, bumping to gcc-9 happened in #21298 IIRC",
      "created_at" : "2021-04-24T07:56:35Z",
